# [Apache2](https://packages.debian.org/stretch/apache2)
Purpose
--
Apache2 is, like lighttpd in Image version <1.5, a webserver. It's used to access smartVISU and other web pages like monitgraph, etc.
It is replaced by nginx in image version 2.2 or higher.

Configuration
--
Config-File: /etc/apache2/apache2.conf 

Options: Define servername, modules, etc. Usually it is not necessary to change anything.
